CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1952, page 13, reads: "Interracial Table - At this table were: Victor E. DeSuites, Anthony Febbaro, Mary Asturl, Joseph DeSimone, Thomas Roche, Richard Taylor, Ora E. Sims, John W. Adams, E. C. Alexander, secretary of the Courier; George G. Price, Emily Ficklin, W. P. Young, A. D. Gaither, Courier circulation manager; A. G. Palamore, Mike Amen, Maria Palamore, Mary Amen, John L. Sander."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including Victor E. DeSuites, Anthony Febbaro, Mary Asturl, Joseph DeSimone, Thomas Roche, Richard Taylor, Ora E. Sims, John W. Adams, E. C. Alexander, secretary of the Courier; George G. Price, Emily Ficklin, W. P. Young, A. D. Gaither, Courier circulation manager; A. G. Palamore, Mike Amen, Maria Palamore, Mary Amen, John L. Sander, seated at banquet table in Syria Mosque for county Republican victory celebration
